Goal: Create a data set that contains data from web on a certain topic.
Step1: 
  For each website, create a JSON object containing
    1) Images (urls or the images themselves) 
    2) Sentences containing a few keywords related to the search topic 
    3) The number of outgoing links. 
    4) Website/post last-modified 
Step 2: 
  Flatten the output of part 1 by sentences and write to a CSV.


